name: podamShouldHandleTheManufacturingOfGenericPojos

testSteps.description: When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.ClassGenericPojo with specific types {class java.lang.String}
Then the pojo uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.ClassGenericPojo@619945 must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.ClassGenericPojo
Then the pojo class java.lang.String must be of the type class java.lang.Class
Then the two objects class java.lang.String and class java.lang.String should be equal

title: Podam should handle the manufacturing of generic POJOs
